## Unit tests

Run all unit tests

```bash
python -m unittest discover -s src/airunner/tests
```

Run a single unit tests `python -m unittest src/airunner/tests/<file_name>`

Example
```bash
python -m unittest src/airunner/tests/test_prompt_weight_convert.py
```
